                "img": "https://arxiv.org/html/2605.16909/2605.16909v1/x1.png",
                "caption": "Figure 2:Overview of the TOBench construction pipeline.\nTOBench organizes tasks into two macro families,Customer ServiceandIntelligent Creation, instantiates them with user instructions, multimodal inputs, executable MCP tools, and domain rules, and validates each task through a generate-inspect-revise loop grounded in actual tool execution.",
